shop owner, right?

I'm sorry. We don't sell any sweets here.

The lord of this town is a good person. The taxes in this town are
surprisingly low.
However... where on earth is he getting the income from to cover that?
Drinking during the day is the best.
Ugh, I want to go to that store again.

This shop is really the best, isn't it? When I eat something sweet,
all my fatigue just disappears in an instant.
You can eat not only bread but also trendy sweets now.
Tapioca drinks... They're popular now, right?

If you plan to eat inside the store, please make a reservation. If you
are taking it to go, please eat it as soon as possible.

Just between us, it seems that there is an entrance somewhere in this
town that leads to a pleasure district.
Hello, this is the town of Castania.
It's dangerous that there have been cases of people going missing.

had to sum it up in one word...
The lord of this place is strangely popular among the nobles.

In this town, clean water flows and the sewage system is well-

Not only in sorcery, but also known as the most talented girl in the

I'm surprised to see that Anastasia-sama, who is said to be one of the
